29/* Maximum packet that we are willing to send/accept */
30#define SFTP_MAX_MSG_LENGTH (256 * 1024)
31
32struct sshbuf;
33typedef struct Attrib Attrib;
34
35/* File attributes */
36struct Attrib {
37 u_int32_t flags;
38 u_int64_t size;
39 u_int32_t uid;
40 u_int32_t gid;
41 u_int32_t perm;
42 u_int32_t atime;
43 u_int32_t mtime;
44};
45
46void attrib_clear(Attrib *);
47void stat_to_attrib(const struct stat *, Attrib *);
48void attrib_to_stat(const Attrib *, struct stat *);
49int decode_attrib(struct sshbuf *, Attrib *);
50int encode_attrib(struct sshbuf *, const Attrib *);
51char *ls_file(const char *, const struct stat *, int, int);
52
53const char *fx2txt(int);
54
